{"tid":2066012,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【港版國安法】批滙豐表態支持立法    英國外相藍韜文：不會為銀行家犧牲香港人","createTime":"2020-06-16T04:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T04:49:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c7b149ac47a5460487dbac22fcada2f2e6aa8124","tid":2066012,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T04:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.takungpao.com/2020/0102/20200102042357405.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.takungpao.com%2F2020%2F0102%2F20200102042357405.jpg&h=eba5933b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多國繼續關注「港版國安法」立法問題，企業的立場亦被放到鎂光燈下。英國外相藍韜文批評滙豐銀行日前表態支持中央訂立「港區國安法」，抵觸英國政府對「港區國安法」的反對立場。又重申英國政府不會為了銀行家的利益而犧牲香港人。而美國駐聯合國大使亦表示，中國加強對香港的管控涉及人權問題，值得在聯合國進行討論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/港版國安法批滙豐表態支持立法-英國外相藍韜文不會為銀行家犧牲香港人-yahoo早報-233802827.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E6%89%B9%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%96%E7%9B%B8%E8%97%8D%E9%9F%9C%E6%96%87%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E7%82%BA%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E5%AE%B6%E7%8A%A7%E7%89%B2%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA-yahoo%E6%97%A9%E5%A0%B1-233802827.html&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aawg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=8fcde7f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/港版國安法批滙豐表態支持立法-英國外相藍韜文不會為銀行家犧牲香港人-yahoo早報-233802827.html</a>"},{"pid":"59ef2f8e77d4443f6723403e9a4fff38eb984d97","tid":2066012,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T04:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yqzY6jk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyqzY6jk.gif&h=f3981308&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b531541d48f18cd695444af83787c81acb8a3a84","tid":2066012,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T04:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj